  "pageTitle": "AI高價值塑膠回收廢棄物分類機",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page product-page-ai\">\n      <section class=\"section split-section\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">AI 廢棄物光學分揀機</p>\n          <h1>AI高價值塑膠回收廢棄物分類機</h1>\n          <p class=\"hero-copy\">WEI LAN AI光學廢棄物分揀器可依材質與顏色辨識PET瓶、HDPE瓶、PP及其他混合塑膠。模組化配置如 支援 自動廢棄物分選系統、MRF設備升級及緊湊智慧回收設施，需穩定且持續分揀。</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n            <a class=\"text-link is-hud\" href=\"/contact\">請求提案</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"../assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.png\" alt=\"AI 可回收塑膠廢棄物的光學分類線\">\n        </picture>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" id=\"models\" aria-labelledby=\"models-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">模型參數</p>\n          <h2 id=\"models-title\">GL01V系列</h2>\n          <p>共用AI分揀平台上的三種配置。依照吞吐量和物料類別選擇。</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-ai\">\n          <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-1\">\n            <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n              <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-01</span>\n              <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V1-5</p>\n                <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">迷你</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <i></i><i></i>\n              </span>\n            </header>\n            <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:35%\">\n                <dt>容量</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.6&ndash;0.8<small>T/H</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:55%\">\n                <dt>動力</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">30<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:38%\">\n                <dt>佔地</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">24<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·8 × 3 m 版面 ·3 m 淨空高度</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:50%\">\n                <dt>分選範圍</dt>\n                <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">5<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明PET·彩色PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合塑膠\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\">PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-2\">\n            <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n              <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-02</span>\n              <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V2-9</p>\n                <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">標準</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <i></i><i></i>\n              </span>\n            </header>\n            <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:58%\">\n                <dt>容量</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.8&ndash;1.2<small>T/H</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:78%\">\n                <dt>動力</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">45<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                <dt>佔地</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">36<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·12 × 3 m 版面 ·6 m 淨空高度</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:90%\">\n                <dt>分選範圍</dt>\n                <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">9<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明PET·綠PET ·藍色PET ·混色PET·白HDPE·有色HDPE·PP ·混合塑膠·拒絕\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 顏色 ·HDPE ·PP ·混合·拒絕</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-3\">\n            <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n              <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-03</span>\n              <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V3-10</p>\n                <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Plus</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <i></i><i></i>\n              </span>\n            </header>\n            <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:95%\">\n                <dt>容量</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">1.5&ndash;2<small>T/H</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                <dt>動力</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">53<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                <dt>佔地</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">51<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·17 × 3 m 版面 ·6 m 淨空高度</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                <dt>分選範圍</dt>\n                <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">10<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明PET·綠PET ·藍色PET ·混色PET·白HDPE·有色HDPE·PP ·PE ·混合塑膠·拒絕\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 顏色 ·HDPE ·PP ·PE ·混合·拒絕</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section sorting-performance-section\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-performance-title\">\n        <div class=\"sorting-performance-head\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">分選效能</p>\n            <h2 id=\"sorting-performance-title\">AI 分選效能建立在可衡量的回收性上</h2>\n            <p>GL01V結合AI識別、光學感測、氣流噴射噴射、循環輸送及數位報告，打造一個緊湊的塑膠回收與MRF升級分揀中心。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorting-feed-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-feed-title\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">給料材料</p>\n            <h3 id=\"sorting-feed-title\">配置為瓶裝及剛性塑膠回收</h3>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sorting-feed-grid\" aria-label=\"公認的塑膠流範例\">\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-clear\"><b>PET</b><small>透明</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-green\"><b>PET</b><small>綠色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-blue\"><b>PET</b><small>藍色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pet-mixed\"><b>PET</b><small>混色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe\"><b>HDPE</b><small>白色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe-colored\"><b>HDPE</b><small>有色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pp\"><b>PP</b><small>剛性</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pe\"><b>PE</b><small>目標</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-mixed\"><b>混合</b><small>塑膠</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-reject\"><b>拒絕</b><small>串流</small></span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorting-data-band\" aria-label=\"GL01V 分選效能指標\">\n          <div class=\"sorting-data-copy\">\n            <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">緊湊型分選中心</p>\n            <h3>在可改裝的架構下，具備高回收資料</h3>\n            <p>Mini、Standard 和 Plus 的配置從緊湊的 試點 產線 擴展到更大型的 MRF 分選升級，同時保持相同的 AI/HUD 操作邏輯。</p>\n            <div class=\"sorting-mode-switch\" aria-label=\"版面狀態\">\n              <span>工作</span>\n              <span>交通</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sorting-data-grid\">\n            <article>\n              <span>分類</span>\n              <strong>10<small>類型 MAX</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>容量</span>\n              <strong>2<small>t/h max</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>動力</span>\n              <strong>30<small>千瓦最小功率</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>佔地</span>\n              <strong>24<small>m<sup>2</sup> Min</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>佈局</span>\n              <strong>滑架<small>安裝</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>快速改裝</span>\n              <strong>17<small>days fastest</small></strong>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorting-smart-panel\">\n          <div class=\"sorting-feature-intro\">\n            <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">智慧機器</p>\n            <h3>操作員準備控制堆疊</h3>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"sorting-feature-grid\" aria-label=\"分揀中心優勢\">\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-ai\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>AI認可</h3>\n              <p>更高的回收價值：AI 能辨識PET、HDPE、PP、PE、混合塑膠，並以較少依賴人工判斷的管道來淘汰。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-air\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>氣流-噴射分選</h3>\n              <p>穩定輸出純度：快速的 氣流 噴射能精確移除目標，同時線路保持連續通量。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-sensors\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>感測器控制</h3>\n              <p>降低純度風險：即時感測器訊號能在輸出品質下降前，暴露識別、壓力、時序及物料流漂移。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-rate\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>96-98% 分揀率</h3>\n              <p>96-98% 分揀性能：手冊中列出的準確度 支援 高純度回收目標，用於塑膠回收與MRF升級。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-robot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>機器人準備佈局</h3>\n              <p>降低勞動壓力：機器人準備佈局留有空間減少手工挑選，隨著物料量增加。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-cockpit\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>數位座艙</h3>\n              <p>更快的決策：即時狀態、警報、運行時間、分選統計、碳排放指標和視訊串流都整合在同一個畫面中。</p>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section dark-section product-process-section\" aria-labelledby=\"plastic-process-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">流程概述</p>\n          <h2 id=\"plastic-process-title\">從給料到數位報告的塑膠回收流程</h2>\n          <p>光學分揀系統圍繞明確的物料路徑組織，讓買家能評估給料、預選、物料分揀、色彩分揀及作業數據在生產線中的定位。</p>\n        </div>\n        <ol class=\"process-timeline\" aria-label=\"塑膠回收流程\">\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-01</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>給料</h3>\n                <p>以受控速率將消費後瓶子或混合的可回收塑膠放入分揀線。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"給料過程影片\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI上料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    你的瀏覽器不會 su 支援 影片元素。\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-02</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>預分選</h3>\n                <p>在下游分揀前，先將金屬 貨櫃 與其他材質製成的瓶子分開。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"預分類流程影片\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI预分.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    你的瀏覽器不會 su 支援 影片元素。\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-03</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>材料分類</h3>\n                <p>依目標樹脂類別分隔塑膠，以提升回收價值並減少人工依賴。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"物料分揀過程影片\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI分拣.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    你的瀏覽器不會 su 支援 影片元素。\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-04</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>顏色分類</h3>\n                <p>依照顏色PET瓶子及其他目標材料分組，專案價值取決於較乾淨的比例。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"色彩分類過程影片\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI出料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    你的瀏覽器不會 su 支援 影片元素。\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-05</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>數位報導</h3>\n                <p>追蹤吞吐量、類別、設備狀態、警示及碳相關操作指標。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"數位報導影片佔位符\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\">\n                  <span class=\"process-timeline-video-tag\">CAM-05</span>\n                  <span class=\"process-timeline-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                  <span class=\"process-timeline-video-label\">影片即將推出</span>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n        </ol>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section product-compare-section\" aria-labelledby=\"compare-title\" hidden>\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">產品比較</p>\n          <h2 id=\"compare-title\">GL01V 與產業基準</h2>\n          <p>WEI LAN AI光學分揀機如何與 對比 比較，典型的分選線，決定推動總擁有成本的指標。</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"product-compare-layout\">\n          <figure class=\"product-compare-explode\" aria-label=\"GL01V爆炸視角\">\n            <div class=\"product-compare-explode-frame\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"爆炸視圖即將推出\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-tag\">爆炸 ·GL01V2-9</span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:18%;--pin-y:32%\" data-label=\"01\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:38%;--pin-y:58%\" data-label=\"02\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:58%;--pin-y:26%\" data-label=\"03\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:74%;--pin-y:64%\" data-label=\"04\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:88%;--pin-y:40%\" data-label=\"05\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-label\">爆炸視角即將登場</span>\n            </div>\n            <figcaption>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-meta\">5 模組化滑橇·標準模具</span>\n            </figcaption>\n          </figure>\n\n          <div class=\"product-compare-panel\">\n            <header class=\"product-compare-panel-head\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-self\"></span>WEI LAN GL01V\n              </span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-base\"></span>產業基準\n              </span>\n            </header>\n\n            <ul class=\"product-compare-list\" role=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-01</span>\n                  <h3>部分與整體比率</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">單位成本的百分比</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:38%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">38%</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">62%</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">較低的備件比率意味著折舊較慢，且壽命 維護 成本較低。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-02</span>\n                  <h3>佔地</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">標準層的 m²</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:55%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">36 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">65 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">滑架安裝布局適合緊湊的 MRF 房間及路邊回收站。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-03</span>\n                  <h3>容量</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">t/h，標準等級</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:88%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.8 – 1.2</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.6 – 0.9</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">優化的訂閱源 + AI識別能提升相同佔地面積等級的吞吐量。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-04</span>\n                  <h3>功耗</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">kW，標準等級</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:60%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">45 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">75 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">按額定吞吐量計算，每噸分揀功率約降低40%。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-05</span>\n                  <h3>運輸與組裝</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">服役天數</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:35%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">3 – 5 天</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:90%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">10 – 14 天</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">預接線滑架模組隨標準 貨櫃 出貨;現場工作僅需螺栓與鋼索。</p>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section ai-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-faq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">常見問題</p>\n          <h2 id=\"ai-faq-title\">AI買家在徵求意見前會問的光學分類問題</h2>\n          <p>這些答案有助於回收業者、EPC團隊及設備採購者評估AI光學分揀機是否適合其物料流及專案階段。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ai-faq-panel\">\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-01</span>AI光學分揀機能分辨哪些材料？</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">該系統設計用於可回收塑膠流，如PET瓶、HDPE瓶、PP、混合硬塑膠，以及顏色基PET分餾物，包括透明、綠色、藍色及混合色瓶。</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span>\n              <span>資料照片或影片</span>\n              <span>目標產出類別</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-02</span>什麼因素會影響AI垃圾分揀機的價格？</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">價格取決於吞吐量、物料類別、分揀模組數量、給料與打包範圍、數位控制需求、安裝 支援，以及專案是否需要與現有MRF設備整合。</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span>\n              <span>目標吞吐量</span>\n              <span>分選模組範圍</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-03</span>一條光學分揀線能處理多少容量？</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">GL01V 車型涵蓋0.6-2 t/h。最終尺寸應檢查 對比 材料組成、污染程度、期望純度、可用可佔地面積及 每日 作業時間。</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span>\n              <span>每日 營業時間</span>\n              <span>可用可儲存佔地面積</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-04</span>該系統能否加裝到現有的回收設施中？</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">當買方提供當前流程佈局、進料狀況、輸送帶高度、控制需求及目標產出時，即可評估整合性。滑架結構 支援 實務改裝討論。</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span>\n              <span>現有路線配置</span>\n              <span>輸送帶高度與控制點</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section ai-rfq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-rfq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ準備</p>\n          <h2 id=\"ai-rfq-title\">準備資料包以AI分揀器尺寸</h2>\n          <p>在報價前將這些輸入資料送出，讓工程團隊能確認分選範圍、設備型號、佈局可行性及整合風險。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ai-rfq-checklist\">\n          <article>\n            <span>01</span>\n            <h3>資料照片或影片</h3>\n            <p>顯示輸送帶的進料流、打包狀況、污染程度及正常運作條件下的顏色混合。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>02</span>\n            <h3>目標吞吐量</h3>\n            <p>確認每小時容量、每日 的營運時間、尖峰負載，以及該線路是否需要一個或多個分揀模組。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>03</span>\n            <h3>產出類別</h3>\n            <p>列出所需的分數，例如PET透明、PET綠色、PET藍色、HDPE、PP、混合塑膠或廢棄流。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>04</span>\n            <h3>現有路線配置</h3>\n            <p>提供輸送帶高度、可用可調整的佔地面積範圍、上游供料方式、下游打包機位置及控制介面需求。</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求工程審查</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">準備檔案包</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
